  "description": "The bioluminescent exciter becomes the primary voice. bioMix at 0.75 with bioBrightness at 2800 Hz creates a flickering bandpass choir above the sub foundation. Two LFOs at coprime rates (0.067 Hz and 0.043 Hz) create irregular trigger patterns — the lanternfish don't synchronize, they converse. The sub sits at -18dB beneath, felt not heard.",
