    "revelation": "Tempora spoke: bioRate 0.067 Hz and lfo1Rate 0.043 Hz are coprime — their least common period is ~330 seconds. For five and a half minutes, the pattern never repeats. The lanternfish choir sings a song longer than any human attention span.",
