    "flock_note": "The Breath discovered that at bioMix 0.75, the exciter IS the sound — the sub is just weight beneath it. The Ear confirmed: bioBrightness 2800 Hz sits exactly in the vocal presence range. The choir is speaking in a frequency band the human ear is most sensitive to.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was bass with bioluminescent seasoning. It is now a choir of alien creatures over a sub-oceanic foundation. The exciter moved from decoration to identity."
